            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"day-3-multi-agent-rag-authority-ranking\">Day 3 \u2014 Multi-Agent RAG &amp; Authority Ranking</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>What you will learn</strong>:</span>\n<ul>\n<li>Why retrieval needs <em>multiple agents</em> \u2014 PO match, vendor risk, and decision synthesis</li>\n<li>How Azure AI Search (hybrid BM25 + vector) surfaces evidence</li>\n<li>How the 4-tier authority policy scores and reorders conflicting sources</li>\n<li>How recency decay down-weights stale facts</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Prerequisite: <code>build/day2/golden_thread_day2.json</code> must exist.</span>\n</blockquote></span>"
          }
